Description: This package provides a way to calculate marginal mediation effects with microbiome data as mediators. The mediator should be compositional data or count data which will be rescaled later on, and could be zero-inflated. The marginal mediation effect will be calculated for each taxon separately. 
URL: https://www.mdpi.com/2073-4425/13/6/1049
